{
  "texts": [
    "Improvement in healthcare industryOne of the industries that stands to gain the most from AI, neural networks, and generative adversarial networks is the healthcare and pharmaceutical industry.",
    "GANs can be used to find tumors in the body.",
    "By comparing images of tumors to a series of photos depicting functional organs, the neural network can be used to find tumors.",
    "The neural net can address risks in visuals and scans of the patient checking for differences between them and the images in the dataset.",
    "When generative adversarial networks are used, cancerous tumors can be found faster and more accurately."
  ]
}